episodes.title: Breaking free from a high control religious group.
episodes.description: In this audio my wife and I give a basic background on Jehovah’s Witnesses and delve into the reasons why they’re a high control religious group aka cult. This speech was held at an adult discussion group so there are questions and answers at the end. I haven’t tested the audio so I hope it comes in clear but everyone who spoke seemed to talk clearly. Enjoy!
